data.value:
Level 3 - The Final Challenge
Hey Matt, this is BARRY KRIPKE. I have a mission for you...
A trusted source has informed me that Sheldon Cooper has a great stack of hand sanitizers, hidden in his apartment - he got waaaay more than he actually needs. Well, I haven't been able to find any at the stores lately, so it's time to take more drastic measures...
Find the 15 hidden hand sanitizers for me and I promise: your actions will not go unrewarded!
Click anywhere on the screen to start...

data.name: level3finish.Text
data.value:
CONGRATULATIONS, MATT, YOU MADE IT! Very impressive.
You know what, I will do more than that... You deserve a more direct and personal thank you.
Click anywhere on the screen to receive your reward...
